{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "本章《第十六回 九阴真经》以“郭黄二人自程府出来，累了半夜，正想回客店安歇，忽听马蹄声响，一骑马自南而北奔来，正渐渐驰近，蹄声斗然停息。”开篇，围绕主要人物的行踪、冲突和江湖牵连展开。中段写到“\"黄蓉道：\"你快按住棺材盖，别让里面⋯⋯里面的东西出来。”，推动人物关系和武功线索变化；后段转向“\"”，并以“郭靖惊道：\"欧阳锋用掌力震破了王真人的灵柩？\"”收束，为后续章节继续埋下因果。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又有了什么奇事？倒也热闹。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岳飞",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "临安府",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我爹爹",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤弟，我在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康脸上一阵热，心中忐忑不安，不知自己适才与欧阳克说话，是否已给两人听到，瞧郭靖脸色无异，心下稍安，寻思：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是我跟你们，是你跟我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉在他耳边悄声道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖自小在马背上长大，马匹多少一听便知，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉忙问：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "另一人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那四王子道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蒙古人叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上去！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你错啦，只有十五人。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "人欢呼叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是啊，你怎么在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拖雷道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这扁毛畜生好坏！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓉儿，留神！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓉儿，你玩雕儿吧，我去杀散金兵！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "中一人叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那里来的狗贼在这里撒野？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这声音好熟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙摆尾",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不快走，都想死在这里么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑问：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "安答，你怎么带了白雕来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "向黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖忙问：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拖雷道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉应声过来，却不见杨康的影踪。郭靖心急，叫道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖大喜，连称妙策。黄蓉甚是得意，笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去将马匹牵到树林子中隐藏起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉喜道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖应声入内。黄蓉在屋顶上叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖一呆，停步道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完颜洪烈道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康默然不语，想起故世的母亲，心中思潮起伏。完颜洪烈缓缓的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完颜洪烈想起十九年前临安牛家村的往事，不由得一阵心酸，一阵内疚，一时说不出话来，过了良久才道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康冷冷的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正自思潮起伏，只听得完颜洪烈道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "富贵不可限量",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想到此处，不禁热血沸腾，伸手握住了完颜洪烈的手，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完颜洪烈觉得他手掌发热，心中大喜，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_hong_lie",
      "speaker_name": "完颜洪烈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么声音？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只听得郭靖与黄蓉一面笑语，搜寻进来。杨康暗叫：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "低声道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康奇道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
      "speaker_name": "杨康",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
      "speaker_name": "杨康",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉见他神色有异，又想起先前他跟欧阳克鬼鬼祟祟的说话，登时起疑，问道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤弟，快搜。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当即去推东边",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康暗暗叫苦，只得假装欣然，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康给她说中心事，脸上一红，怒道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤弟不必介意，蓉儿最爱闹着玩。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
      "speaker_name": "杨康",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊，他在那边！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "冷笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你别弄鬼。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，那奸贼定是躲在棺材里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
      "speaker_name": "杨康",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥小心，莫要是僵尸作怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "颤声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "靖哥哥，慢着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "眼见黄蓉吓得玉容失色，便纵身跃上棺材，安慰她道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是女鬼！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨贤弟，咱们掀开棺盖瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓉儿，快来，你瞧是谁？",
      "tone": "焦急",
