      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
      "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我给坏人拿住了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
      "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "涌泉穴",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她有心让两人一倾相思之苦。那知穆念慈板起了一张俏脸，竟毫无笑容，说道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康登时满脸通红，背脊上却感到一阵凉意：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖一笑，随她走出。黄蓉走到前院，悄声道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
      "speaker_name": "杨康",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妹子，我⋯⋯",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打起架来了，可得劝劝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穆念慈怒道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
      "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穆念慈怒道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
      "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穆念慈本已委顿不堪，此时急怒攻心，",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉高声叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你把杨大哥那柄短剑给穆姊姊罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从怀中掏出那柄朱聪从梅超风身上取来的短剑，剑柄上刻有",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她想郭杨二人的短剑既分属二女，姻缘已定，无可更动，不由得大为放心，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖奇道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉伸了伸舌头，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她本想说",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姊姊使不得！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姊姊，姊姊！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里的景致好么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桃花岛女主冯氏埋香之冢",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "管他是吉是凶，我总是跟去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这调子怎么如此好听？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是什么猛兽？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大椎穴",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那长须人似乎不信，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那长须人脸色忽变，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那长须人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖恭恭敬敬的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那长须人点点头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长须人又",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此外还有谁传过你功夫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九指神丐洪恩师⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那长须人脸上登现欣羡无已的神色，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随即摇头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一时想不透其中原因，双目从上至下，又自下至上的向郭靖望了两遍，右手伸出，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖凝力发劲。那长须人手掌略缩，随即反推，叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一想到",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，不禁心头一寒：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "人微笑问",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜我是谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "长须人笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖沉吟道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "长须人呵呵笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊，你是周伯通！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有东西吃啦！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄姑娘呢？她怎不来瞧我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖听了，半晌做声不得，心道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 802,
      "line_end": 802
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "忽地掩面大哭，乱扯自己胡子，叫道：",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子依前辈吩咐就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老顽童",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 838,
      "line_end": 838
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "笑什么？快跟着念。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖今日与老顽童周伯通义结金兰",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连小老鼠小乌龟也打不过",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "罢了，罢了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 844,
      "line_end": 844
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后来怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 862,
      "line_end": 862
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通沉吟片刻，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 864,
      "line_end": 864
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖忧形于色，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 870,
      "line_end": 870
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 872,
      "line_end": 872
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜我怎么会在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 876,
      "line_end": 876
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
